title: rFactor the ultimate car collection + mapPlugin
description:
=========================================
rFactor 1255: the ultimate car collection
=========================================

English


==========================
About this Jimbus edition:
==========================

- Custom installer compressed.
- The game is updated to the last available version, the 1255.
- Tons of extra cars and tracks are included.
- Multiplayer works.
- Several mods are included. Some of them are installed ("MapPlugin 106 and XD 214"), some not ("RealFeel").


=============
Instructions:
=============

1. Run "setup.exe" to install the game.
2. Use the shortcuts the installer creates.

Warning!: the installation process is long and needs 52 GB of free space.

Q: Does the multiplayer work?
A: Yes, it does.

Q: Does it work under Windows 8.1?
A: Yes, it does.

Q: 52 GB?! How is it possible?!
A: It is because of the extra cars and tracks included. You won't be disappointed.


Notice this is not an update but the full game. Do not install it over an existing installation
